name: Webinato
overview:
Webinato is owned by omNovia Technologies founded in 2004, a world leader in web and video conferencing software. You may visit our parent company at www.omNovia.com.

We have created Webinato with the goal to provide a simple platform that allows you to create high quality, easy-to-use and brandable webinars within minutes. By adding movies to the mix and taking more polls, you make your webinars more engaging and hence more successful when it comes to the messages you are trying to convey.

We have a global foot-print with a worldwide network of servers that constitute our cloud-based web conferencing system. Over the years we have built a significantly reliable infrastructure with multiple layers of redundancies and backup that has made our system have a unique 100% uptime.
